Package org.barghos.core.api.tuple

This package contains all interfaces for tuples.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ITup2dR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 2-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup2dW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 2-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup2fR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 2-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup2fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 2-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup2R
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 2-dimensional tuple.
    ITup3dR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 3-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup3dW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 3-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup3fR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 3-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup3fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 3-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup3R
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 3-dimensional tuple.
    ITup4dR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 4-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup4dW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 4-dimensional double tuple.
    ITup4fR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 4-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup4fW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an 4-dimensional float tuple.
    ITup4R
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an 4-dimensional tuple.
    ITupdR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an n-dimensional double tuple.
    ITupdW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an n-dimensional double tuple.
    ITupfR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an n-dimensional float tuple.
    ITupfW
    This interface grants access to all writing methods of an n-dimensional float tuple.
    ITupR
    This interface grants access to all reading methods of an n-dimensional tuple.
